@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Health check — confirm the app is up
GET {{host}}/health

### 2. Ingest sample documents (run ONCE)
POST {{host}}/ingest

### 3. Ask the demo question (RAG)
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Onde as piranhas vivem?"
}

### 4. Ask another question — try your own
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Which predators live in the rainforest?"
}
